quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Back then, every time Uncle Hong finished work, he'd come here for a warm bowl of Jinzhou Stew.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"My grandfather always said that food shortens the distance from home, and also brings people closer together.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"Jinzhou Stew isn't just a simple dish. It's a bond that connects people.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"And for Uncle Hong, it's probably even more meaningful, since the people sitting with him here have changed since his day.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003},{"text":"He's the only one left.","quest_name":"Hidden Dangers in Peaceful Life","quest_id":134000003}]}